OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776760724
OL,3,CFire destroys 'irreplaceable'
OL,4,Csaltmarsh in Kent as arson
OL,5,Cinvestigation begins
OL,7,FA fire has destroyed a saltmarsh
OL,8,Fhabitat in Kent which the county's
OL,9,FWildlife Trust has described as
OL,10,F"irreplaceable".
OL,12,FThe blaze spread across over 300
OL,13,Fmetres of Sandwich and Pegwell Bay
OL,14,FNational Nature Reserve, one of Kent's
OL,15,Fmost important and internationally
OL,16,Fdesignated wildlife sites.
OL,18,FKent Wildlife Trust said there was
OL,19,F"extensive damage" to the site.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
