OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776760724
OL,3,CFire destroys 'irreplaceable'
OL,4,Csaltmarsh in Kent as arson
OL,5,Cinvestigation begins
OL,7,FKent Police said an arson
OL,8,Finvestigation has begun.
OL,10,FThe fire occurred during the breeding
OL,11,Fbird season and the Trust believes it
OL,12,Fis likely to have destroyed nests,
OL,13,Fkilled reptiles, and caused
OL,14,Fsignificant disturbance to wildlife
OL,15,Fthat depends on the surrounding area.
OL,17,FIt added that the loss of saltmarsh is
OL,18,Fparticularly serious as the habitat
OL,19,Fcannot be replaced and is home to rare
OL,20,Fplants and animals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776760724
OL,3,CFire destroys 'irreplaceable'
OL,4,Csaltmarsh in Kent as arson
OL,5,Cinvestigation begins
OL,7,FEmma Waller, Senior Planning & Policy
OL,8,FOfficer at Kent Wildlife Trust,
OL,9,Fsaid:"Pegwell Bay is one of the most
OL,10,Fsensitive and important coastal sites
OL,11,Fin Kent.
OL,13,F"Its saltmarsh is an irreplaceable
OL,14,Fhabitat that supports rare species and
OL,15,Funderpins the functioning of the wider
OL,16,Fecosystem.
OL,18,F"We are devastated by the damage
OL,19,Fcaused by this fire, particularly
OL,20,Fduring the breeding bird season when
OL,21,Fwildlife is at its most vulnerable.
OL,26,@qD@FOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776760724
OL,3,CFire destroys 'irreplaceable'
OL,4,Csaltmarsh in Kent as arson
OL,5,Cinvestigation begins
OL,7,F"The likelihood of destroyed nests,
OL,8,Floss of reptiles, and widespread
OL,9,Fdisturbance is deeply concerning.
OL,10,FIncidents like this also set back
OL,11,Frecovery in habitats that are already
OL,12,Ffragile and slow to regenerate."
OL,14,FIn a statement, Kent Police said:
OL,15,F"Kent Police was called to separate
OL,16,Freports of bins being set alight in
OL,17,FCliffsend, Ramsgate, including in
OL,18,FChapmans Fields and Pegwell Bay Nature
OL,19,FReserve at around 8.30pm on Sunday 19
OL,20,FApril.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1776760724
OL,3,CFire destroys 'irreplaceable'
OL,4,Csaltmarsh in Kent as arson
OL,5,Cinvestigation begins
OL,7,F"The fires were extinguished each time
OL,8,Fby Kent Fire and Rescue Service with
OL,9,Fno reported injuries. Officers
OL,10,Fattended the scene and an arson
OL,11,Finvestigation is ongoing."
OL,13,FKent Fire and Rescue Service said:
OL,14,F"Kent Fire and Rescue Service was
OL,15,Fcalled to reports of marshland alight
OL,16,Fin Sandwich Road, Ramsgate.
OL,18,F"Three fire engines attended, and
OL,19,Fcrews used main jets and hose reel
OL,20,Fjets to extinguish the flames.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
